Perms:

The easiest way to grant SeCreateSymbolicLinkPrivilege is to start gpedit.msc, go down to
"Windows Settings"->"Security Settings"->"Local Policies"->"User Rights
Assignment", then find "Create symbolic links" and add whatever users and groups you want[1].

or (cygwin): editrights -u $USER -a SeCreateSymbolicLinkPrivilege

